# Minimal universal .gitignore shipped by claude-setup. Kept deliberately
# generic: operator tooling and private state (CLAUDE.md, .githooks/, private/,
# etc.) are ignored locally via .git/info/exclude instead, so this committed
# file never names them. Add language-specific entries (Rust target/, Node
# node_modules/, Python __pycache__/) when you know what the repo ships.

# Environment + secrets
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
.credentials.json

# Editor + OS leakage
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/
.vscode/

# Build artefacts (this repo ships Rust + Node)
/target/
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo
__pycache__/
*.pyc
